## Technology Requirements

When analyzing features, consider these React 19 + React Router 7 equivalents:

| ISML Pattern | React Equivalent |
|--------------|------------------|
| `<isslot>` with content-assets | Fetch content asset body via API, render with component |
| `<isslot>` with products | Fetch products in loader, render ProductGrid |
| `<isslot>` with categories | Fetch categories in loader, render CategoryTile grid |
| Static `<div>` sections | Direct JSX with Tailwind CSS |
| `<form>` elements | `useFetcher` + resource route action |
| `${Resource.msg()}` | i18n with `useTranslation()` or loader data |
| `${URLUtils.url()}` | React Router `<Link>` or route path |

